parameters:
Luuna and the others, defeated by Hilda, retreated with their lives
barely intact.

However, during their retreat, they were cursed by Hilda with the
"Succubus Curse." Luuna and Becky became extremely lewd in nature.

To lift the "Succubus Curse," Luuna and Becky consulted Rade, but Rade
too was infected by the curse. The "Succubus Curse" was a contagious
spell.

It was revealed that to break the "Succubus Curse," they must have
sexual intercourse with unwanted men, conceive, and give birth.

And so, Luuna, Becky, and Rade ended up on the brothel's stage to be
impregnated by men. Due to the aphrodisiac magic, all three had become
nymphomaniacs.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Sigh... The only way out of this situation is to be
impregnated... Let's resign ourselves to it. \C[24][Becky]\C[0] Well... We have no
choice but to become their playthings. We'll be toyed with until
they're satisfied. Rade: Why do I have to go through this too... It's
so cruel...
Afterward, Luuna and Becky were able to regain their original powers.
Rade was still under the curse of stone.
Rade also managed to regain her original powers.

Then, to challenge Lucia and the others again, they infiltrated deep
into the castle of the dark night.
